    "description": "swissTLM3D Railway contains the path of the railways with narrow-gauge and standard gauge. All tracks are captured in the sections with multiple tracks and in the areas of a station. swissTLM3D Railway is part of the dataset swissTLM3D. With a high accuracy and the incorporation of a third dimension, swissTLM3D is the most extensive 3D vector data set of Switzerland.",
